- list of snmp servers in ini file. For each:
    - url of mib
	- snmp access config
    - list of oids to collect (?)

- definition of table(s) where to store polled data

- cronjob that polls servers in list

- fetch function to do an snmp get on the desired server/oid

- module-view to show collected data, with zoom over time

- module-view to do real-time snmp get
